This game is much, much more than I expected out of a bowling game app. At first, I was very stubborn to leave Doodle Bowling behind, which is another great bowling app, but I found Galaxy Bowling to be the most realistic of all the comparative apps I've yet tried. I'm stuck on Ten Pin and also the Ten Pin Tournament, but there's also the very challenging and often annoying 100 Pin Challenge that makes you want to play and play, over and over again.  Try this app and purchase all the games.  There are a few more that are unique and from our historical past. If you like bowling, you'll love this app. I    certainly do. Oh, and I'll give you a heads up: The longer you play, the better your score...
